OL,3,C'National crisis': Tougher sentences
OL,4,Cfor jealous ex-partners who kill
OL,6,FChanges to domestic homicide laws are
OL,7,Fset to come into force in 2025, ITV
OL,8,FNews Reporter Amy Lewis explains
OL,10,FJealous ex-partners who kill or
OL,11,Fstrangle their victims will receive
OL,12,Ftougher jail terms as part of what the
OL,13,Fgovernment call its continued
OL,14,Fcrackdown on violence against women.
OL,16,FThe government is introducing tougher
OL,17,Fsentencing rules for murders involving
OL,18,Fstrangulation or when the killing is
OL,19,Fconnected to the end of a
OL,20,Frelationship, following a review of
OL,21,Fdomestic homicide laws.
