OL,6,FA minister said the changes for
OL,7,FEngland and Wales, expected to come
OL,8,Finto force next year, would ensure
OL,9,Fpunishments reflect the severity of
OL,10,Fthe "most abhorrent" crimes.
OL,12,FThe Law Commission, an independent
OL,13,Fbody that reviews the law and
OL,14,Frecommends changes, has also been
OL,15,Fasked to review the overall sentencing
OL,16,Fframework for murder and the law of
OL,17,Fhomicide.
