OL,3,C'National crisis': Tougher sentences
OL,4,Cfor jealous ex-partners who kill
OL,6,FThis comes in response to issues
OL,7,Fraised by campaigners, including how
OL,8,Fdiminished responsibility is
OL,9,Fconsidered and whether current
OL,10,Fsentencing rules properly reflect the
OL,11,Fseriousness of domestic murders.
OL,13,FDiminished responsibility is a legal
OL,14,Fdefence allowing offenders to claim
OL,15,Freduced liability due to mental
OL,16,Fimpairment or medical conditions.
OL,18,FThe Ministry of Justice said 85
OL,19,Fpeople, mainly women, are killed by
OL,20,Ftheir current or ex-partner each year,
OL,21,Fmostly in the home.
