OL,6,FAlex Davies-Jones, the minister for
OL,7,Fviolence against women and girls,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The level of violence against
OL,9,Fwomen is a national crisis which this
OL,10,Fgovernment is determined to tackle,
OL,11,Fand that includes ensuring the
OL,12,Fpunishment fits the crime for the most
OL,13,Fabhorrent crimes.
OL,15,F"I want to pay tribute to all those
OL,16,Fwho campaigned for change in this
OL,17,Farea, including the Joanna Simpson
OL,18,FFoundation, Killed Women, and the
OL,19,Ffamilies of the victims of the
OL,20,FNottingham attacks."
